  "body": "A good amount of charts are randomly generating passwords when they are run. This causes issues when upgrading charts, causing passwords to be regenerated. \r\n\r\nWhat I would like to see is something along the lines of:\r\n\r\n{{- if .Release.Upgrade }}\r\n{{- end }}\r\n\r\nAnother approach could be to expose the release number:\r\n{{- if .Release.Revision == 1 }}\r\n{{- end }}\r\n",
